definitions.definition: A village and civil parish in South Hams district, Devon , England ( OS grid ref SX7964 ) .
A village and civil parish in Tewkesbury borough , Gloucestershire , England ( OS grid ref SO8925 ) .
A village and civil parish in West Northamptonshire district, Northamptonshire , England , previously in Daventry district ( OS grid ref SP5461 ) .
A village and civil parish north of Trowbridge , Wiltshire , England ( OS grid ref ST8560 ) .
A rural locality in Kentish Council area, Tasmania , Australia .
